    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver. The exterior is flawless, with a deep shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in showroom condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. You can expect a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was first sold.",
